<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Verify Your Email - PilotPanel</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Outfit', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #F7F7F7; color: #393E46; margin: 0; padding: 40px; }
    .container { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 40px; border-radius: 18px; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
    h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #393E46; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #686D76; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #393E46; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #929AAB; margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Verify Your PilotPanel Account</h1>
    <p>Thank you for registering with PilotPanel. To complete your setup, please click the verification button below:</p>
    <a href="<%= verifyUrl %>" class="btn">Verify Account</a>
    <p style="margin-top: 25px; font-size: 14px;">If you did not request this registry, please ignore this email.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      Powered by PilotPanel Minecraft Hosting.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
